Results.ReviewText: I have a medical condition which means I have to be at hospital very early 3 times a week and these are a great way of taking an early morning coffee. I have the heated thermos-type cups but the Azera actually feel like a take away coffee from a store. They are slightly on the expensive side but often on offer at one of the supermarkets so I keep a watchful eye and buy in bulk!
Results.Title: Morning Pick me aup

Results.ReviewText:
I thought these would be good for when I travel on a train but haven't got time to buy a latte before boarding. Little did I know how tasty they are and how quick to make, just fill up with hot water, stir and go! 
I now won't be buying an expensive latte from the station cafe.
Results.Title: Great for on the go

Results.ReviewText:
Have been buying this for a while now and no other instant latte comes close.
The taste is excellent,just wish our local supermarket would stop running out of stock! Have tried buying in bulk but it's so nice I end up drinking far too many in a day!
Results.Title: Best instant coffee

Results.ReviewText: I bought this product a month ago, & although I'm not a massive coffee drinker i love the taste of this instant latte. It is smooth and rich where it is needed to be. I would highly recommend this product to anyone looking to buy it!
